gate: OPEN
task: S74-TD1
title: Fix Internationalization Implementation
description: |
  The i18n implementation from S72-T09 is not working properly. Fix all issues:
  - Verify i18n.ts is properly initialized with react-i18next
  - Check that locale files (en.json, ru.json, uk.json) are properly loaded
  - Ensure language switching works in the UI
  - Verify server locale sync from GET /ws/settings
  - Test all UI components are using translation keys
  - Fix any missing translations or broken i18n hooks

acceptance:
  - Language switching works seamlessly in the app
  - All UI text is translated when switching languages
  - Server locale preference is respected on app start
  - No hardcoded strings remain in the UI
  - Console shows no i18n-related errors

requires: []
estimated: 4 hours
